.be/A5Owrq0UEqY</a><br />\nMission 11-14<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6fIdM_Z_liM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6fIdM_Z_liM&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK%2FilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=bdbffaf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6fIdM_Z_liM</a>"},{"pid":"93266aa54757d74bc21df796967ca0591223be52","tid":1698191,"uid":105546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:21:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/921885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/921885</a> Hitman2全暗殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/930875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/930875</a> Hitman2只穿西裝的無聲殺手 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/950819\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/950819</a> JUST CAUSE 4<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/972483\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/972483</a> Devil May Cry 4<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cjjswS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cjjswS</a> 生化危機2重製(Leon)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ckmqMS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ckmqMS</a> 生化危機2重製(Claire)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cnzmNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cnzmNS</a> 還願Devotion<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/crwGLS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/crwGLS</a> Devil May Cry 5"},{"pid":"f3e56a0f39bc3bff2791503367341db82db50f5b","tid":1698191,"uid":105546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa437feb8f004961100ce4c7e04ba3c3e3fb7e2","tid":1698191,"uid":105546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"